des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Ferroli devices. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Ferroli Smart" app in Google Play or iOS App Store then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our "Ferroli Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Appstore, Google Play or iOS App Store then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search "Ferroli Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable "Ferroli Smart" skill, and you'll be navigated to "Ferroli Smart" login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the Gas Water Heater.”
“Alexa, turn off the Gas Water Heater.”
“Alexa, set the Gas Water Heater temperature to 50.”
“Alexa, what is the temperature of the Gas Water Heater.”
“Alexa, turn on the Gas Water Heater bathtub mode.”
"Alexa, set the Gas Water Heater water volume to 200."
"Alexa, turn on the preheat of the Gas Water Heater."
"Alexa, turn on the Gas Water Heater timer switch."
